---
// src/components/RentVsOwn.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight text-display">
                Why pay Google "Rent" every month?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Most businesses spend thousands monthly on ads just to stay visible. The moment they stop paying, the phone stops ringing. <strong>Stegg is different.</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5">
                    <i data-lucide="banknote" class="w-32 h-32 text-slate-900"></i>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-red-50 text-red-600 rounded-lg">
                        <i data-lucide="refresh-cw" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">The "Ad Trap"</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
                        <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Cost Model</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-red-600">Monthly Rent</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
                        <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Cost for 1,000 clicks</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-900">~RM 5,000 <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">(Recurring)</span></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm pb-2">
                        <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">If you stop paying?</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-red-600">Traffic hits 0 instantly.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-5 text-sm text-red-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    "It feels like being a tenant. You pay Google everyday, but you never actually build an asset."
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-800 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden transform md:scale-105 z-10 ring-4 ring-slate-200/50">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10">
                    <i data-lucide="building-2" class="w-32 h-32 text-white"></i>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/50">
                        <i data-lucide="gem" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">The Stegg Asset</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm border-b border-slate-700 pb-4">
                        <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium">Cost Model</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-green-400">One-Time Build</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm border-b border-slate-700 pb-4">
                        <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium">Cost for 1,000 clicks</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-white">RM 0 <span class="text-slate-500 font-normal">(Forever)</span></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm pb-2">
                        <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium">If you stop paying?</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-green-400">Traffic keeps coming.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-5 text-sm text-blue-200 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    "This is like buying the shoplot. You pay us once to build the digital infrastructure, and you own the traffic forever."
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">The Business ROI Calculation</p>
            <div class="inline-flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-4 md:gap-8 bg-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
                <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                    <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">1 New Client</span>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Avg Value</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:block text-slate-300">
                    <i data-lucide="equal" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                    <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">RM 3,000+</span>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Direct Revenue</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:block h-8 w-px bg-slate-200 mx-2"></div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium max-w-[200px] leading-tight text-center md:text-left">
                    Just <span class="text-slate-900 underline decoration-blue-400 decoration-2">2 new clients</span> covers the entire cost of the website.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>